data.description: Down right nice at 961 Lincolnshire Circle! It's a luxury to be steps away from the playground, access to extra parking, no rear neighbors, only one-side neighbor, spacious driveway on a premium lot, Solar owned. Yes, there's more! With over 2200SF this 2-story contemporary was built in 2020 in the Gated Cerrada Community with 4 bedrooms (1-down) and 3 full baths. Chef-inspired kitchen has plenty of granite counters, an island with storage, gas stove, refrigerator, sizeable food pantry and spacious eat-in area. Spread out and enjoy the bright living room. Bonus space in the loft upstairs.  Ensuite in primary bedroom upstairs has a walk-in closet and an extra closet, large shower stall with seat and dual sinks. Inside laundry room upstairs with washer and dryer. Finished landscaping in front yard has fire pit at patio and rear yard has retaining walls, patio and privacy.  Exclusive amenities to Lincoln Crossing Clubhouse include: exercise gym, indoor/outdoor pools, sports court, tennis and more. Conveniently located near shopping center, restaurants and Hwy 65.
